com.paypal.selion.platform.mobile.ios

Class UIAElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.platform.mobile.ios.UIAElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UIAutomationElement
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UIAAlert, UIAButton, UIANavigationBar, UIAPicker, UIASlider, UIAStaticText, UIASwitch, UIATableView, UIATextField

    public class UIAElement
extends Object
implements UIAutomationElement
    The UIAElement is the super class for all user interface elements in the context of the Automation instrument for automating user interface testing of iOS apps. This interface defines more general methods that can be used on any type of user interface elements.

      • findElement

        public org.openqa.selenium.WebElement findElement(String locator)
        Description copied from interface: UIAutomationElement
        Finds the corresponding web element using the string locator. The locator is internally converted into By entity and fed to RemoteWebElement.findElement(By) for further processing.
        Specified by:
        findElement in interface UIAutomationElement
        Parameters:
        locator - A String that represents the means to locate this element (could be id/name/xpath/css locator).
        Returns:
        Instance of WebElement found by the locator.
